'Cel' may refer to: *Cel, a transparent sheet on which objects are drawn or
painted for animation purposes *Cel programming language *Cel Publishing, an
imprint of VDM Publishing devoted to the reproduction of Wikipedia content
* 'cel', the ISO-639 code for Celtic languages
* Cel (goddess), the Etruscan goddess of the earth
